Jeff,

You can try something like this and you should be able to pick up all
classes ending with Test in a particular directory.

    &lt;junit showoutput=&quot;true&quot; printsummary=&quot;true&quot;&gt;
     &lt;formatter type=&quot;xml&quot; usefile=&quot;yes&quot;/&gt;
        &lt;batchtest&gt;
        &lt;fileset dir=&quot;${junit.classes.path}&quot; &gt;
        &lt;include name=&quot;**/*Test.class&quot;/&gt;
        &lt;/fileset&gt;
        &lt;/batchtest&gt;
    &lt;classpath location=&quot;${junit.base.path}/jar/wsm-junit.jar&quot;/&gt;
    &lt;classpath refid=&quot;unittest.classpath&quot;/&gt;
    &lt;/junit&gt;

Hope that helps,
Harshal



